OOC: Well whatever :) I said sorry cause I kept calling it the Obylisk.

BIC:

Grimlock arcked in a different direction from the cannons, turning his
body sideways, and begining to soar to the side. He then aimed his
rocket launcher and pulled the trigger, sending to rockets on a trail of
fire towards the ship. "Grimlock Obliterate you if you not return
Autobots." he screamed.
